        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Asserting Basic Common-sense Coordination in School Discipline Act or the ABCs in School Discipline Act</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 to prevent state and local educational agencies that receive certain federal funds from implementing a policy that&nbsp;discourages: (1)&nbsp;schools from reporting a disciplinary action to law enforcement, or (2) law enforcement from&nbsp;making&nbsp;certain&nbsp;arrests.</p>]]></text>
